                        <desc>Nasta'liq and Shikastah Amiz. The MS appears to have been copied from one in a confused state. There are some gaps. The name of a copyist, 'Abdallah son of Mulla Shaikh appears on f155a. The final portion of the work now starts on f164b and ends with f185. See (Morley's?) pencilled notes, and those on ff209b, 210a, 211a, 215a, 227b, 228a, 287b.</desc>
